    "description": "Keep precious finds safe and organized with ASR Outdoors Six Inch Storage Collection Container with Lid. Designed for the field explorer, this compact yet durable container is perfect for securely storing valuable items like gold, fossils, gemstones, rocks and other treasures discovered on your outdoor adventures. <br><br>The sturdy construction and secure, easy to use lid, ensure that found items stay protected from dust, dirt and potential loss or damage. Whether you're a geologist, gold prospector, fossil or gemstone hunter, rock collector and more, this container is a must have tool for keeping discoveries in pristine condition until you're ready to inspect, display, or store them long term.<br><br>Specific to gold prospecting, this bottom collection storage container has been specifically designed to seamlessly fit on and stack with ASR Outdoors six inch mini gold classifier screens; together they provide a complete solution for material sorting and collection in the field.<br><br>Compact enough to fit in your backpack, yet tough enough to handle rugged terrain, it’s the ideal solution for keeping your treasures safe while you continue your exploration.",
